value:
This may not be my typical weapon,
but my brother Hríd and I trained
with bows when we were young.$k$pI should be of some assistance to
you still.

Nifl is all but closed off due to the
snow this time of year. Askr is so
warm and cozy by comparison!

Thank you for inviting me to
accompany you to the shrine. I
already know what I'll wish for...$k$pAnd I hope your wish comes true,
too.

Seeing the dawn of the new year
from the sky is like nothing else.$k$pYou can join me up there if you'd
like. Don't worry, I'll hold the reins!

There is never enough time. We must
take life one day at a time and stride
steadily toward our goals.

I come with a greeting for the
new year from your dear friend
$Nf.

I'm so happy right now. Recalling this
feeling will carry me through the year!
I never want to forget this sensation.

This means I'm not yet strong
enough...

Surely a good sign... I'll make this
year better than the last.

I am Fjorm, second princess of Nifl. I
hear that some people plan their
entire year on New Year's Day.$k$pLet's set our goals together, shall we?

To be able to visit you for the new
year is exactly what I wanted. It's
made me very glad.$k$pI've been reflecting on my actions of
this past year, and I've decided to
embrace new goals for this new year.$k$pI don't want to spend my days idle.
I will continue moving forward, and
I'll do all I can with the time I have.$k$pAnd also... I want to help you in any
way I can. Even more than I did last
year.$k$pWell then... Shall we head to the
shrine? Let us both make new
promises for this new year.
えいっ！
やぁっ！
きゃああっ！
だめですっ…！
Strike like Leiptr!
Let us celebrate!
Happy New Year!
I pray for good fortune.
The year's just begun...
Umm...
I have never worn anything quite like this before... How do I look?
Oh, you startled me! I'm glad it's just you.
Are you familiar with new year's traditions like these?
I hope it is not too much to ask, but... Will you take my hand?
Whenever I am with you, I feel such warmth.
My wish for the New Year has already come true, hasn't it?
Spending the New Year with you...makes me very happy.
Of course.
A new year!
Let's go together.
